{"id":"1sf54fz","title":"Wheel strategy is boring… until it’s not","author":"Amanda-Medina","created_utc":1775588035,"score":0,"selftext":"I’ve been running the wheel for a while and honestly… most days are pretty boring.\n\nCollect some premium, wait, repeat.\n\nThen days like this happen.\n\n\\+$22k today.\n\nNot saying this is normal (it’s not), but it kinda makes me question why more people don’t run this strategy consistently.\n\nI’m not doing anything crazy either just sticking to a few names I’m comfortable holding and letting the premiums stack.\n\nFeels simple… maybe too simple?\n\nI've created a free group where I share my strategies. If you're interested, please leave a comment or send me a private message, and I'll invite you to join and share with you.","url":"https://i.redd.it/u2rlv59tettg1.jpeg","comments":[{"id":"oev9ohp","author":"Ok_Beginning_8126","body":"I'm very interested and would like to learn more about your strategyplease send me an invitation.","score":1,"created_utc":1775592483,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"oevg5pk","author":"Amanda-Medina","body":"Send Invitation","score":0,"created_utc":1775594737,"is_op":true,"replies":[]}]},{"id":"oevvwtu","author":"grimmjoww1983","body":"Share the group please","score":1,"created_utc":1775599517,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"oew3ruf","author":"Amanda-Medina","body":"Send Invitation ","score":1,"created_utc":1775601980,"is_op":true,"replies":[]}]},{"id":"oewapb4","author":"Next-Counter-8835","body":"I’m definitely interested and would like to know more about this.","score":2,"created_utc":1775604101,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"oewhb7r","author":"Amanda-Medina","body":"ok","score":1,"created_utc":1775606198,"is_op":true,"replies":[]}]},{"id":"oewjxkf","author":"[deleted]","body":"[removed]","score":1,"created_utc":1775607064,"is_op":false,"replies":[]},{"id":"oex89qt","author":"Poliphone","body":"I’m interested ","score":1,"created_utc":1775615098,"is_op":false,"replies":[{"id":"oezllgk","autho